<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
最近都沒有看到你呢，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你怎麼了嗎？
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是因為看書看得太入迷了？<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵！<delay frames="40" />
如果可以遇到那麼有趣的書，<delay8 />
那真是太幸福了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
最近都沒看見你，<delay8 />
真的讓我好寂寞喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是<delay20 />都自己一個人邊<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay8 />
邊期待著哪天能跟你見面耶，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好久不見了，<delay frames="40" />
你最近是不是很忙呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />上見不到
<tag a="110" b="4" />的身影……<delay20 />
讓我覺得有點寂寞呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay20 />
好久不見了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有聽別人說，<delay8 />
你最近過得不錯喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過沒什麼機會跟你說話，<delay8 />
讓我覺得有點寂寞呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得我們好像很久不見了呢，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你最近過得好嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那～個<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
我本來有話想跟你說的，<delay8 />
可是我是想說什麼來著<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />時間一久，<delay8 />我就不小心
忘了要說什麼呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
我們有一段時間<delay8 />沒說到話了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天<delay8 />非常謝謝你<delay8 />
找我說話喔！<delay frames="40" />跟你說到話，
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就覺得安心多了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>